      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think this interval should enforce some reasonable lower bound. The default is as in VSCode 180sec, which already feels fairly low. But setting this to 1 sec is likely going to create trouble for someone.",
      "revId": "8a734e16478c6baf7d7f03ae11105d9fe03778c7",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
