      "writtenOn": "2026-03-24T23:29:05Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I would rather use a default of 1h and don\u0027t allow intervals shorter than 5 min. Our git servers are used by thousands of developers, if 5000 developers start fetching every 3 minutes this causes 30 requests/sec on the server.",
